title: Hour 3 - More Draymond Reaction, Let's Ride, Woody Paige
itunes:title: Hour 3 - More Draymond Reaction, Let's Ride, Woody Paige
description:
Dan and the Danettes continue to react to the leaked video of Draymond Green punching Jordan Poole at Golden State Warriors practice, and wonder if Denver Broncos QB Russell Wilson will ever stop saying, 'Let's ride!' Plus, Woody Paige drops by and said both Wilson and Matt Ryan look like they should retire.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
